Title: Trajectories
Plot: When a second murder suddenly occurs at an active crime scene, Al and Carrie must wade through hundreds of bystanders to uncover if it was retribution or an unrelated attack.
GuestStars: C.S. Lee, Danny Flaherty, Maria Elena Ramirez, Greg Serano, Dascha Polanco, Iris Delgado, Robert Funaro, Jonathan Hogan, Jennifer Restivo, Erik Jensen, Tino Sutras, Luke Rosen
